description:
This week on Unqualified Anna and Sim sit down with one of the kindest people in the world, the magnificent RuPaul (RuPaul’s Drag Race, RuPaul's Drag Race: All Stars, What's the Tee?)! RuPaul gives Anna and Sim their drag names, they talk about sexuality, spirituality, their first albums and play a winning round of Would You Rather! Later they call Jo, who doesn’t know what to do about her partner's close friendship with an ex, and Jackie, who finds out the guy she’s been talking to is secretly an NFL player!

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
